version_description: All of the lyrics are included, with the chords above them, and chords are placed more accurately over lyrics. Is also a slightly different version of the song, not the live version, but the album version.
Corrected chord placement, seperated song into sections, added strumming pattern (based on ukelele in the recording) and other information.
Complete and well-aligned chords for the whole song including instrumental parts / suggestions for playable voicings.
This version is mostly based on this cover from youtube with a few fixes, perhaps look there for strumming pattern. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aOIHXM7WG3I.
Other versions contain incorrect chords and do not include the entirety of the song.
